Table 2: Recommended DEXILANT SoluTab Dos age Regimen by Indication in Patients 12 Years of Age and Older 
For patients with moderate hepatic impairment (Child-Pugh Class B), the recommended dosage is a 30 mg DEXILANT capsule or DEXILANT SoluTab once daily for up to 8 weeks. The use of a DEXILANT capsule or DEXILANT SoluTab is not recommended in patients with severe hepatic impairment (Child-Pugh Class C)[see Use in Specific Populations].
